snippet.title: SERANU - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Find lost treasure, fame and fortune in the ruins of the Lost City! SERANU brings spelunking to the PC in a single-player adventure full of puzzles and mysteries.

Wishlist SERANU on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1987100/SERANU/
